    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! This beauty has been such a reliable ride for me and it's still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved, drives super smooth, and the interior is nice and clean. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for a dependable, great-looking vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
